caption: Nice place with number of galleries, different types of art and beautiful setting. It's recommended to visit.

In Montparnasse this unexpected and hidden alley next to a auto repair place is a hidden gem. Right out of the 19th century it holds places pursuing the artistic ideals in a setting that helps support those ideals. At the moment (September 2019) the alley is u der repair so some of the charm is lost, but it will soon be different. I am teaching at an art atelier called Figura...an atelier of representational painting. Wonderful. Support the arts!
